OL,5, Boris Becker, the six-time Grand Slam  
OL,6, tennis champion, was using his business
OL,7, account as a "piggy bank" to pay for   
OL,8, personal expenses, a court has heard.  
OL,10,FHe spent money from his business       
OL,11,Faccount on his children's school fees, 
OL,12,Fdesigner clothes and shopping at the   
OL,13,Fluxury store, Harrods, jurors heard.   
OL,15,FThe 54-year-old, who commentated for   
OL,16,Fthe BBC last year, is on trial at      
OL,17,FSouthwark Crown Court charged with 24  
OL,18,Foffences under the Insolvency Act.     
OL,20,FHe denies all charges.                 
